  ('new-museum', 'New Museum', 'museum', 'The New Museum of Contemporary Art is a museum at 235 Bowery, on the Lower East Side of Manhattan in New York City. It was founded in 1977 by Marcia Tucker.', 'The New Museum of Contemporary Art is a museum at 235 Bowery, on the Lower East Side of Manhattan in New York City. It was founded in 1977 by Marcia Tucker.', 'Manhattan', 'Lower East Side', '235 Bowery, New York, NY 10002', 40.7223376, -73.9928905, 'https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/place-photos/AJRVUZOw50zCGR4lDOeJ33WIu-c4F2d3hKCJarCeJP8fyLD-jwCEDjActGTtpQ8bEKrCpDh6qLoRKlBkrcZOd1lOj_Hdc_ErdiMzpFx3IEzhjytzxyIPxHLNF7oHIg9ZSCyPCrmlrlZ5eYE7ZXgv=s4800-w800', ARRAY['https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/place-photos/AJRVUZOv8PjhY5kOXyDMC85ZqjuQTNcvzw_8fVRKS7-ilP6yfA8c6AJyH1cLnjfUwPpTU13uunKg7n1F94XF0MBsVYRJkzvxBGLaHx6ahrTj-gkg_tOh9O9N2tkUOyC0S3KTFB92DR10mHpO1Wko=s4800-w800', 'https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/place-photos/AJRVUZMGO4uYqzVrk08CLvlWUFzgzzwkt1-jAM8dy6YAv2R3ZuCHVI8lyaI8U17C9t5Y_VqHPmSMpDl8wnbTmWU2wXwTi_7Ic4KJ08pCKwMhpqP0_oHj0NvMOr1HScsSZS9wBfjYKpMKM2RI6NUH=s4800-w800', 'https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/place-photos/AJRVUZP_4S0bczr-LS6fwdMYX5QeMluEpvxtRSVGBITqrPbvwfETojCEscVyxJjCGcp3QTOYgXpLXlpmkdaHKpVK7YBLGihZgq7OBX2p3FEjror9jQ9ATLxqtqJyPGhqV-cXuH8Vxg6LrEudOjTLFA=s4800-w800']::text[], '{"mon": null, "tue": [["11:00", "18:00"]], "wed": [["11:00", "18:00"]], "thu": [["11:00", "21:00"]], "fri": [["11:00", "18:00"]], "sat": [["11:00", "18:00"]], "sun": [["11:00", "17:00"]]}'::jsonb, 'Tue 11:00–18:00; Wed 11:00–18:00; Thu 11:00–21:00; Fri 11:00–18:00; Sat 11:00–18:00; Sun 11:00–17:00', 'ChIJlaRS3IVZwokR2llMD6dCt-U', 4.1, 2688.0, NULL, NULL, NULL, 90, 'Bowery (J,Z)', 'https://www.google.com/maps/embed/v1/place?key=AIzaSyC1g4kcF24ADMnnTKrUSuvmbM1iGQ1qdGA&q=place_id:ChIJlaRS3IVZwokR2llMD6dCt-U', 'https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=New+Museum&query_place_id=ChIJlaRS3IVZwokR2llMD6dCt-U', 'https://www.newmuseum.org/', '+1-212-219-1222', ARRAY['art_museum', 'mus