  ('museum-of-arts-and-design', 'Museum of Arts and Design', 'museum', 'The Museum of Arts and Design (MAD), based in Manhattan, New York City, collects, displays, and interprets objects that document contemporary and historic innovation in craft, art, and design. In its exhibitions and educational programs, the museum celebrates the creative process through which materials are crafted into works that enhance contemporary life.', 'The Museum of Arts and Design (MAD), based in Manhattan, New York City, collects, displays, and interprets objects that document contemporary and historic innovation in craft, art, and design. In its exhibitions and educational programs, the museum celebrates the creative process through which materials are crafted into works that enhance contemporary life.', 'Manhattan', 'Midtown-Times Square', '2 Columbus Cir, New York, NY 10019', 40.767375, -73.98194720000001, 'https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/place-photos/AJRVUZPzSxHDdcXqnml73K-tuNemU6B7ZHPpWWVIMQ9ACOHWHhE-ncSA7zAvX48okcMjlEWuVWMPsSexzVqcYafA2RrUGi-IXUI3Y6GJ7tQitnEsTAkClXVsL9O1pbhVBsbtdVWKFLhuhtsOLt0p=s4800-w800', ARRAY['https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/place-photos/AJRVUZMFXfOI7UGp-sRqCCxXvCurxWj7drXPyh2M1ewOjVMN6OVrtkmqBR5jXDJRDrPWYkf8BB9gSHxXgrntOp-yyjH1J5zaNi9n8SzpzSgZanuCtaHVvE_qAyQFJzqsa6vA9rDNWFZQ3wq0Nd3u6A=s4800-w301', 'https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/place-photos/AJRVUZP7Y1eSILKX6jwR3qj0CxnuDevdVwrXIqkw57Ri-Iuk0D_uZb4QM3gSPbT-bAe3_PDja24AEsQaRtZnrQnUpWcA14r-Qdkj7QLVI9waDHHM2pPgq7MUxCXOiZa5iXvXds-f7z26eDNjRaF8=s4800-w800', 'https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/place-photos/AJRVUZOeGkmq-PEuyhJkQfw8-oW-NoSIGkA0A6VuW72eqJoCJMzVgNeQ9RBi7n8c8p5pHmRTNmXh7R1u6sk8RTyX2DkLVyJNUlymVBN-gBAZq1HrOBZexFr4Ul5ybOlwVMYWn6PtqVYKNhXVtfF5=s4800-w800']::text[], '{"mon": null, "tue": [["10:00", "18:00"]], "wed": [["10:00", "18:00"]], "thu": [["12:00", "20:00"]], "fri": [["10:00", "18:00"]], "sat": [["10:00", "18:00"]], "sun": [["10:00", "18:00"]]}'::jsonb, 'Tue 10:00–18:00; Wed 10:00–18:00; Thu 12: