  ('museum-of-sex', 'Museum of Sex', 'museum', 'The Museum of Sex, also known as MoSex, is a sex museum dedicated to preserving and presenting the history, evolution, and cultural significance of human sexuality. The museum focuses on a variety of sexual preferences and subcultures, including lesbian and gay history and erotica, BDSM, pornography, and sex work. Due to explicit content in its educational exhibits, visitors must be at least 18 years old. Despite initial controversy from religious groups and rejection for non-profit status by the New York State Board of Regents, the museum has operated without significant opposition since opening and has hosted interfaith events exploring sexuality and religion.', 'The Museum of Sex, also known as MoSex, is a sex museum dedicated to preserving and presenting the history, evolution, and cultural significance of human sexuality. The museum focuses on a variety of sexual preferences and subcultures, including lesbian and gay history and erotica, BDSM, pornography, and sex work. Due to explicit content in its educational exhibits, visitors must be at least 18 years old. Despite initial controversy from religious groups and rejection for non-profit status by the New York State Board of Regents, the museum has operated without significant opposition since opening and has hosted interfaith events exploring sexuality and religion.
Located at 233 Fifth Avenue at the corner of East 27th Street in Manhattan, New York City, the museum opened on October 5, 2002, founded by Daniel Gluck. In 2024, the museum expanded with a second location in Miami, Florida.', 'Manhattan', 'Midtown South-Flatiron-Union Square', '233 5th Ave, New York, NY 10016, USA', 40.7440291, -73.9872529, 'https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/place-photos/AJRVUZPX7tFlNJTMTV96a6U08pO-Dt5-bB8MfunZ9YNArNNblEoWT6aAENH4SnupYo8NrnaqbbR2ALo8zPz7auujJyElwLMsjdDno7E9aaVVjrPaNRWQnNl8a71iFAXitDur3T9IcSJuHP989DT-sg=s4800-w800', ARRAY['https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/place-photos/AJRVUZM41IqXIjgQo0OcCp3gVLpgkHElg8PPV5FhdulDaURdNFlMVnsrCw9eoTct7KBXD9E5eI3xLD-sbmifkyLfcFBoIa8IMw7NjcNDRjhbivgGBElr7gD6QbAkNWLPaaTBg9mcUgjonD2PznHY=s4800-w800', 'https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/place-photos/AJRVUZPeZQPijRIJ0XzS3ZTn1358TV-qKPCn8HnqydzsvmyJpZDbpw4HRJBO-6COt2AtKVmVg3UpYYhnNerrJxV2HFTskl_-oBzdijpFAMIMLFwojOx7hI6SpoxelApwPK_8TbXAjo6GOaXWZmdfzw=s4800-w800', 'https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/place-photos/AJRVUZP3asQfa98vMkAni2Kgy2TJ4z073Sj8NSijHMbdqbK8cWsqbC1TRL3rAccd19s7owiUeE9EeSnrFt3jafTjtIwrnXClCMOCNzvu7-BGSw9AY3ynujJKIM3mHJUEgj-0C4p76l_qitK96J-CcA=s4800-w800']::text[], '{"mon": [["13:00", "22:00"]], "tue": [["13:00", "22:00"]], "wed": [["13:00", "22:00"]], "thu": [["13:00", "22:00"]], "fri": [["13:00", "24:00"]], "sat": [["12:00", "24:00"]], "sun": [["12:00", "22:00"]]}'::jsonb, 'Mon 13:00–22:00; Tue 13:00–22:00; Wed 13:00–22:00; Thu 13:00–22:00; Fri 13:00–24:00; Sat 12:00–24:00; Sun 12:00–22:00', 'ChIJR026QqZZwokRgLuHSIZNIKM', 4.4, 6021.0, ARRAY['wheelchair']::text[], NULL, NULL, 90, '28 St (R,W)', 'https://www.google.com/maps/embed/v1/place?key=AIzaSyC1g4kcF24ADMnnTKrUSuvmbM1iGQ1qdGA&q=place_id:ChIJR026QqZZwokRgLuHSIZNIKM', 'https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=Museum+of+Sex&query_place_id=ChIJR026QqZZwokRgLuHSIZNIKM', 'https://www.museumofsex.com/locations/new-york-city/', '+1 212-689-6337', ARRAY['museum', 'indoor', 'wheelchair']::tex