  ('highbridge-park', 'Highbridge Park', 'park', 'Highbridge Park is a public park on the western bank of the Harlem River in Washington Heights, Manhattan, New York City. It stretches between 155th Street and Dyckman Street in Upper Manhattan. The park is operated by the New York City Department of Parks and Recreation. The City maintains the southern half of the park, while the northern half is maintained by the non-profit New York Restoration Project. Prominent in the park are the Manhattan end of the High Bridge, the High Bridge Water Tower, and the Highbridge Play Center.', 'Highbridge Park is a public park on the western bank of the Harlem River in Washington Heights, Manhattan, New York City. It stretches between 155th Street and Dyckman Street in Upper Manhattan. The park is operated by the New York City Department of Parks and Recreation. The City maintains the southern half of the park, while the northern half is maintained by the non-profit New York Restoration Project. Prominent in the park are the Manhattan end of the High Bridge, the High Bridge Water Tower, and the Highbridge Play Center.', 'Manhattan', 'Highbridge Park', 'W 190th St &, Amsterdam Ave, New York, NY 10040, USA', 40.8537599, -73.9257492, 'https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/place-photos/AJRVUZN9MvNUbKSJFrIXX6MRty2CS1F4yoB7REOLrq25ND2hcanaernu-1tXBviogvd9VOPD9LYBdElnJQQyAKqv4LTQ4LNxFsN9N5BfjjlQfztOtTiwor-kOYnTuOGpbfu1AFqyBgibKBLz_vo82A=s4800-w800', ARRAY['https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/place-photos/AJRVUZPe0nwOOmlIBOBo4uLOkU5ckMY2orEkP8zHOybim5f4Cj2LxpUogNlsiRbQyB_p_R78y5Wb9AtZu4c5ygsynFCcko_1cf1cpp67SpGeT8FtoMSmn8UOI2h9GUH6DV4gfQPva4PRRwx4CPze=s4800-w800', 'https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/place-photos/AJRVUZN894GI2ToZx_bYi4UjSnmi5s6pKI5g2EIuPsztAwTTQC9Q0GyAjdCtGXQ3q2FN7uXvWysgNPEPiyvmmzaMHS8TUmii3vG4zcPWJihepncWoM2bZHo99ValW8WZ-enACyPSnLJdBgLPJ54z=s4800-w800', 'https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/place-photos/AJRVUZNLJUrjdCbjwZ9ogKAaIHGly6lb5fUXBDq-Mznqe-21rHtNaCHNYmCPou99OyeFsOvHXDKCD1