  ('bethesda-fountain', 'Bethesda Fountain', 'landmark', 'Bethesda Terrace and Fountain are two architectural features overlooking the southern shore of the Lake in New York City''s Central Park. The fountain, with its Angel of the Waters statue, is located in the center of the terrace.', 'Bethesda Terrace and Fountain are two architectural features overlooking the southern shore of the Lake in New York City''s Central Park. The fountain, with its Angel of the Waters statue, is located in the center of the terrace.
Bethesda Terrace''s two levels are united by two grand staircases and a lesser one that passes under Terrace Drive. They provide passage southward to the Central Park Mall and Naumburg Bandshell at the center of the park. The upper terrace flanks the 72nd Street Cross Drive and the lower terrace provides a podium for viewing the Lake. The mustard-olive colored carved stone is New Brunswick sandstone, with a harder stone for cappings, with granite steps and landings, and herringbone pattern paving of Roman brick laid on edge.', 'Manhattan', 'Central Park', 'New York, NY 10024, USA', 40.7743214, -73.97088289999999, 'https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/place-photos/AJRVUZMkUovgMN3bB80y7jTyBSVxHj9NhWIpaCpn0qLnXY6otfUxnbslVBrda2VHro_yuUQY5PBKiaNW0YnkNPXlJ3Rqwqw4z0bcf_s9ZwfUc1tq143UIGbconX0HPIT_wTIFBh85eHTGA0uNHz4=s4800-w800', ARRAY['https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/place-photos/AJRVUZNFxB3cnlTsaBOGt4ENA7Dj8GBobC7m4HaAKhW7IunB2OaVodMtGBMuY1AoowVZt_KunkgYq7HC7qxwvW2cP6b8fAvNV0UWxMmuvjMv4MhOt-rFjzKSQJXVD9-TAr6t7khQtiJMFCekc7Ao=s4800-w800', 'https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/place-photos/AJRVUZMv52o_b1yFxPlhvyAGuBVnyz4UJeRTaN_yBGP-IbIAThlShzNxiMZ32mmLhTP9cOYMl_vaOWfrWlYr38c68YCmqWOmpaEPsRCkrJQmiBR4BEdarHMoU-ZJdKNXoR1ANBiUaz99w8cB0O4_gA=s4800-w800', 'https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/place-photos/AJRVUZMukCihq3AKQenVCs95i-tmNSKYii3200DZ9-IFA340clQKRgwmY7ixBSQ6vFqo9RJ8k3G-IbF-ztJZmyz3f24DGdR7jaJ552X0vvU6JA7OWAmbBN-D055yjdyq0qrpzVoDG3D9dwkeM-xeqw=s4800-w800']::text[], NULL, NULL, 'ChIJZaQT5aVZwokRffG4eQn-mrA', 4.8, 1417.0, NULL, NULL, NULL, 45, '72 St (C,B)', 'https://www.google.com/maps/embed/v1/place?key=AIzaSyC1g4kcF24ADMnnTKrUSuvmbM1iGQ1qdGA&q=place_id:ChIJZaQT5aVZwokRffG4eQn-mrA', 'https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=Bethesda+Fountain&query_place_id=ChIJZaQT5aVZwokRffG4eQn-mrA', 'https://www.centralparknyc.org/locations/bethesda-fountain', '(212) 310-6600', ARRAY['tourist_attraction', 'attraction', 'indoor']::text[]),
  ('westside-theatre', 'Westside Theatre', 'other', 'The Westside Theatre is an off-Broadway performance space at 407 West 43rd Street between Ninth and Tenth Avenues in the Hell''s Kitchen neighborhood of Manhattan, New York City. The building houses two auditoriums: the Upstairs Theatre, which seats 270, and the Downstairs Theatre, which features a thrust stage and has a seating capacity of 249. Formerly known as the Chelsea Theatre Center and the Westside Arts Theatre, the building was renovated in 1991.', 'The Westside Theatre is an off-Broadway performance space at 407 West 43rd Street between Ninth and Tenth Avenues in the Hell''s Kitchen neighborhood of Manhattan, New York City. The building houses two auditoriums: the Upstairs Theatre, which seats 270, and the Downstairs Theatre, which features a thrust stage and has a seating capacity of 249. Formerly known as the Chelsea Theatre Center and the Westside Arts Theatre, the building was renovated in 1991.', 'Manhattan', 'Hell''s Kitchen', '407 W 43rd St, New York, NY 10036, USA', 40.7596056, -73.99254169999999, 'https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/place-photos/AJRVUZPk9zWUF5sDUB0RMYE9F6NhibIQ2heQ-DpWpP-twyzs-n3FGUQVFrQA9IiLi4AUs-q-HZGJz-yTvD1f55nnpOVbDCf0JDZ8Zb9yq5UejqXUh5L41WH0ZtL72RI7tXTwbYR8ygpet_IwP1VZ=s4800-w800', ARRAY['https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/place-photos/AJRVUZO0L9V1h4tB4vHzGmi9qF5jq_ixzmJStcgbW5-vLF7W9xaa8ESODzbKr24K_txxTsESgv3i5WdZYRAS6giFF0t6Bdg5RZTzKeRXnt4iXgAvjvUVH53ovRqLgQsuX9rFSB-MlSCKIwO39u92Ls38G6A-=s4800-w800', 'https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/place-photos/AJRVUZN9c9DIlg9AvE0Jtt6E7dUjuEYIvgeP3i5Cu08L_gJ1i20uY3JHEkQjrAOICPNF6QK054G8NKpYRpBNvWDtwxaqFhiVUDotwguWHmeXikFqiN85UrCLEy7rIzgz1EtjMg930JvnwLyEZeMVwg=s4800-w800', 'https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/place-photos/AJRVUZMRw5jBXtYLcAFIByB12im3D1x4vuo-3DkyjKrTzyBP2vniK1NSTAavGsaMw7Cz7aoiZaA1_PJp7BaJDOmCdAZAIjMDdxGJV7VqsxoVmxuLjUF0g31xaVRE0UiPPKEo6gzND8sbclwo0G4T=s4800-w800']::text[], '{"mon": null, "tue": [["12:00", "20:00"]], "wed": 